  <brief_title>Virtual Reality Training Program for Ambulatory Patients With Chronic Gait Deficits After Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of a Virtual Reality Training Program for Ambulatory Patients With Mild-to-moderate Chronic Gait Deficits After Stroke</official_title>
  <sponsors>
